# Biobase Performance UI Rule

When implementing Biobase performance analytics, follow `docs/roadmap.md`, `docs/features/performance_dataset_categories.md`, and `docs/ui/clarion_interface_doctrine.md`.

Default UX: one Performance Review page with top summary, sticky category rail, and expandable category sections. Optional deep-dive screens are allowed; forced separate category pages are not the default.

Design standard: compact, value-first, low cognitive load, no card soup, no duplicated labels, semantic color only, thin charts, screenshot review before completion.
